{"title":"一条大道","authors":["李冰"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":3,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条大道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李冰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太行山，万丈高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半山腰里一条道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁锹叮当人吆喊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修路的人儿有千万。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太行山下是平原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条大道直向南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺着大道向南瞅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修路的人儿望不到头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男男女女满脸汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁锹镐头明闪闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年青的小伙子胳膊粗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起镐头气不喘；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年青的媳妇手拿锹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子放在路旁边；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿红的女娃娃唱着歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一锹一锹把土垫；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大伯，领着队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手拿丈尺量路段。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“老大伯，我问你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大道修到那里去？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女娃娃，我问你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修好大路到那里？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大伯，哈哈笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女娃娃，唱得好："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“大路修到黄河边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好让咱大军下江南！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好大道，阔又平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大车卡车都畅行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“闪开道，闪开道！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们的队伍过来了”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大炮、小炮一串串，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弹药粮草装得满，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年青的战士跟后面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身上背着“手机关”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过来个战士站路边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自家的村子在眼前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"押粮草，送子弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路过家门顾不得看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东瞅西瞅四处寻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看见村里修路的人；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东瞅西瞅四处寻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一眼看见了老母亲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两步奔到娘跟前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉住妈妈笑盈盈："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“妈妈啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修路你也上了阵？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈拉住儿衣襟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从头打量到脚跟："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“孩子呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们年青的上前线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡亲们已把路填平！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“妈妈啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任务紧，赶路程，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天顾不得进家门。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“孩子呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村村挑战修路忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天顾不得给你蒸干粮”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“妈妈呀，别挂心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放全国就回程。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“孩子呀你快起身！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看咱的大路修得平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早一天捉住蒋介石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回家再吃团圆饼”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小女娃娃拍手喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“大哥呀，快快赶！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大路宽又宽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运炮弹，不觉难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快叫老蒋吃鸡蛋！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大伯，笑盈盈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“孩子呀，迈步行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用问，不用停，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这条大路通南京！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}